Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:35.96,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:43.63,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 拉面好了
